result.adr_address: G/F, 19 Chiu Lung St, Central, Hong Kong
result.formatted_address: G/F, 19 Chiu Lung St, Central, Hong Kong
result.name: Wing Lok Yuen Restaurant

reviews.text:
Right in the middle of central off an Alley near queen's Road. Steep stairs takes you to a basement old school HK canteen.

Traditional tea sets, they are famous for the double hotdog with relish sauce.

However since we got a booth, tried the lunch Ox tongue with tomato sauce and rice. The HK milk tea is nice and frothy.

Finished up with a corned beef and egg sandwich, great homey taste.

If you are looking for a loud, sharing tables, good local HK canteen, then this is the place for you.

Famous for hot dog. Bun is good and sauce is sweet.
Only thing is the price is abit pricey. I ordered a breakfast set with extra sausage HKD41.

Nice toast set. Small cosy place worth visiting. Love the underground setting. The uncles are nice and accommodating. Smile and they will smile at u. Don’t worry about language barrier they will slowly take ur orders.
Be ready to eat with many others on the same table. Food is decent but I wouldn't intentionally go there
Love the hotdog sauce. Also the tea is pretty good. Environment is a little shabby, but still acceptable.

result.formatted_address: G/F, 19 Chiu Lung St, Central, 香港
result.name: 永樂園熱狗餐廳

reviews.text: 有名的中區熱狗🌭️店
永樂園出名熱狗， 亦都是大多數中環 中午時分 必到的餐廳之一， 餐飲都是一般茶餐廳 種類， 炒粉麵， 午餐、下午茶餐…… 都是 快速 飽肚 的最佳地方。
熱狗醬味道幾十年不變，但今次腸仔比較硬
除咗佢借單唱熱狗好味之外佢嘅魚柳包係用返個熱狗醬做
雖然係上環，都唔係咁嘅價錢街邊質素丫？垃圾
